skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: spare min
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Listen to any call that was published on SpareMin through this Alexa skill. You can listen to any popular calls that were created on the platform, listen to someone's latest content, or listen to your own content.
Explore topics and follow other SpareMin users and we'll curate a playlist for you.
In order to host your own content, you must have a call and record on the SpareMin app.
